    "This prevents the neural network from excessively co-adapting and relying too heavily on specific features, limiting its ability to recognize only the training data.",
    "Dropout not only addresses overfitting but also contributes to developing more resilient networks.",
    "By forcing the network to operate with various samples, Dropout promotes robustness.",
    "This approach facilitates the averaging of predictions and reduces test time [27], as highlighted in Fig. 3, to mitigate overfitting in the network.",
